Harfang is a lightweight Web development framework written in the haXe language (http://haxe.org), currently aimed at the PHP target.

The framework's documentation can be found there : http://haxe.org/com/libs/harfang.
A tutorial to build your first application with the framework is also available there : http://haxe.org/com/libs/harfang/tutorials/quickstart

Enjoy!